data.description: Welcome home. Located off the Powers corridor, close to Woodmen and Black Forest Rd., sits this beautiful 4 bedroom, 4 bath, 2 story home with fully finished basement and an attached 2 car garage. Nestled in a quiet neighborhood in a desirable location close to hospitals, shopping, schools and more, this 2 story gem backs to open space and features timeless style and craftsmanship. Upon entry you're greeted with newer flooring, a half bath on the main level, coat closet and small entryway to the family room. The family room extends high ceilings and large windows that filter great natural light, and an open and spacious flow and feel. Through the family room you enter the spacious kitchen and dining room area with walk-out to the private backyard and deck. The kitchen extends plenty of counter space complete with a large island, 36" and 42" cabinets with crown molding, and beautiful wood floors. As you venture upstairs, you'll discover 3 bedrooms and 2 additional bathrooms. The primary bedroom features a coffered ceiling, 2 walk-in closets, and an adjoining 5 piece master bath! The laundry is located upstairs, along with plenty of storage and closet space. As you head down to the fully finished basement you'll discover more storage, the 4th bedroom, and full bath, plus a huge living room/great area. This home comes with a brand new roof (August 2023), updated windows, and immense pride in home ownership! It's truly a MUST SEE, and won't last long. Don't hesitate! Call today to schedule your private showing.
